HOLOTYPE
. — 
NHG 22279
: neurocranium with nasals, ascending fragments of maxilla and premaxilla, damaged frontals (the lateral part of the sop is missing), parietals, occipitals, squamosals, petrotympanic complexes, fragment of hyoid and four cervical vertebrae. Most of the rostral elements anterior to the vertex, and the dentaries, are missing (
Figs 2-4
; 
7-9
; 
11
; 
12
).

